data.definition: korean woman who is a gold digger
data.description: 김치 is kimchi, and 녀 means women. Used to refer to Korean Women who only loves money. (Sexual discrimination and Racism)
data.exampleSentence:
돈많은 남자만 만나는거 보니 김치녀네
(She's a gold digger. She only meets rich guys.)
